-- MOVES-Medley promotes Brian Dohmen to head direct lending in eastern U.S.
-- 
-- Mon Aug 18, 2014 07:57AM EDT
-- None



Aug 18 (Reuters) - Asset manager Medley LLC, owner of business development company Medley Capital Corp <MCC.N>, said it promoted Senior Managing Director Brian Dohmen to head direct lending in the eastern United States.

Dohmen, who has 17 years of experience, previously managed business development for Newport Realty LLC, a Chicago-based real estate firm.